{
  "stem": "13251.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He's in Israel.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I kind of lost track with him, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Let's see, what else?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Trying to think.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "About that.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, in London I went-- for some reason I ended up going-- the home was given two scholarships to a private, orthodox school.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Don't ask me why they sent me and this other kid.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was the last one who was a suitable candidate, because I was kind of a little bit rebellious, I guess.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But yeah, I went to the orthodox school, which I hated because I had all these religious studies in addition to normal studies.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Plus, it cut into my sport activities.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't have that much time for that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There's one friend, very close friend that I made in that school, that I'm in touch with to this day.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "His name is Leon.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He comes from a big family, and I knew his whole family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I think, let's see-- one, two-- about four of his family used to go to that school, and I know them all.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But with him, I've kept in touch.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He lives in London, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He still lives in London.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, he went to regular public school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had everything I wanted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] He had all the sports, and he didn't care for sports.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had an indoor swimming pool in his school, wow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He had all the things that I would have liked to have had.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After he finished school, he went to training up north England, a place called Thaxted, where they had-- oh, we joined Bnei Akiva, which was a Jewish Zionist group, OK?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after that-- it was like a continuation of that-- he went to farm training in Thaxted, up north.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
